{
  "texts": [
    "Consider two solutions f 1 (t, A, w) and f 2 (t, A, w) of either the uncontrolled model (13) or of the controlled one (27), such that their corresponding initial conditions satisfy f in 1 (A, w) = f in 2 (A, w) for a.e.",
    "A ∈ R and w ∈ I.",
    "If the function K[f](t, w) is analytical in t for a.e.",
    "w ∈ I, then K[f 1](t, w) = K[f 2](t, w) for a.e.",
    "w ∈ I and any t > 0.Proof."
  ]
}